WEBVTT

00:01.400 --> 00:04.074
I don't know whether you know that there's been a shooting.

00:05.440 --> 00:08.558
It was the detective we saw near the Falls Road on Sunday night.

00:08.720 --> 00:10.791
<i>James Olson was a married man, Stella.</i>

00:10.960 --> 00:14.192
You were a married man when you spent a night in my bed.

00:14.360 --> 00:17.717
I'd like you to meet the girls of Monroe Air.

00:18.160 --> 00:20.152
- It was an accident.

00:21.360 --> 00:23.477
<i>All I want is for somebody to hold me...</i>

00:24.640 --> 00:26.518
<i>..tell me I'm gonna be all right.</i>

00:26.680 --> 00:28.751
- Liz needs help, Jimmy.
- Stay away from my wife.

00:28.920 --> 00:30.559
Or I'll kill you and your wife.

00:30.720 --> 00:32.040
And your kids.

00:32.200 --> 00:34.840
<i>He clearly has a victim type.</i>

00:35.000 --> 00:37.993
They are not victims of chance, they are victims of choice.

00:38.160 --> 00:41.756
<i>It's possible that he's out there stalking his next victim now.</i>

